{
  "stem": "5313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it started to get light in the morning and the owner of the house came out and they saw us and started to beg us to run away from here, while they're going to call the-- the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I couldn't blame them, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason why they was-- you know, if they saw us over there, they probably would kill them, you know, so we had to get away from there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, you know, we was trying to get away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we find it that on a run in a little wooded hill, we saw, you know, our people marching.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we get back to our people again, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had no choice that we started to march again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we hit Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hit Romania.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went through Hungary, and all the way to the border Germany, to the border of Germany, which they putting over there, they put us as a cattle, they're putting into a cattle--",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--car, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the way they took us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would say it took us about four months, four, five months we was walking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would say probably a day or so, you know, which we was cattles, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have no restroom, no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So many people even died there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they started to select people to the left, people to the right, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- people to the left, you know, they took us through a line where we have to undress.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took all the jewelry or anything valuable we had with us, you know, we have-- they took everything else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We was given some striped kind of clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
